A hanging length of chain, 32 map units tall. It can be combined with [[Classes:ZChainBit64|ZChainBit64]], [[Classes:ZChainEndHeart|ZChainEndHeart]], [[Classes:ZChainEndHook1|ZChainEndHook1]], [[Classes:ZChainEndHook2|ZChainEndHook2]], [[Classes:ZChainEndSpike|ZChainEndSpike]] and [[Classes:ZChainEndSkull|ZChainEndSkull]] to form long hanging chains by carefully adjusting the height value of each in the map editor.
